{"tid":1411773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求置頂]一齊入黎討論下一次罷工計劃","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:03.000Z","uid":206224,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e47683ee25afeef8f016d4662a056bc887e1a7e","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"今次罷工+被罷工成效都算係幾好<br />\n但依然有一部份人照樣返工，其中一個原因係為政治原因而罷工係不受勞工法例保障，好多人都驚被秋後算帳<br />\n所以我強烈建議下一次罷工，<span style=\"color: red;\">各行各業應該要好好計劃下，將罷工包裝成為非政治原因</span><br />\n<br />\n第57章 《僱傭條例》 第9條指出，僱主無權以僱員參加罷工終止其僱傭合約<br />\n而罷工具有《職工會條例》(第332章)第2條給予該詞的涵義，僅指同一行業員工為爭取更好僱傭條件而舉行嘅罷工<br />\n換言之，你因為爭取雙普選而罷工，你老細可以炒你。<span style=\"color: red;\">但你為左爭取加人工，你就有免死金牌。</span><br />\n<br />\n以會計界為例，如果會計師巴絲想參與下一次罷工，但又驚被老屎忽partner炒，你地可以開個telegram group，然後組織自己行業嘅罷工，<span style=\"color: red;\">口號就係 &quot;我要真普選，同埋加人工&quot;</span><br />\n其他專業界別，例如測量師、律師、銀行家等等，都可以效法。<br />\n<br />\n各位下一次罷工，識做啦？"},{"pid":"9d759d96859a64622026fb1e35af9ee0d47fa0ae","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d715b550e52f94d131eef8902ed2cd7a5bde8ad","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02152bff463ff30205cbf76353462ef85f9a8f1f","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb448d4922e90e3316b45df1a6e6700222f6b5e1","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbf99b05c3d4497b9286a722917e8af5ca4f98e","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f6e87495b91662e2c5d6d000540c8a34d770fc","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd48760d4655e3a020931820fc9f668403ff3fd","tid":1411773,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工 撳錢 不消費 走資呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"d145857c349e4df9f46b8fef9636020e94655d2a","tid":1411773,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立即去撳錢 拎現金保障自己！金融式抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411732</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"8558ea1b45af12c9b25015ff967898128da1c44b","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2285de6fdf8bde934fa09dbf68e56579dd30c8d3","tid":1411773,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c1733f66047f36f350a514eac2ec2f21aa57343","tid":1411773,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6412e6cf6760485ed066437b17630bac1b29f46a","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b0d39a2c606014ea5f5009659da2a085fcac20d","tid":1411773,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"reference:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/57/s9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkli